lending.getBonusRewards: Get bonus rewards in all markets
subprotocol.rulesText: Nomos Protocol is an infrastructure open to everyone. Anyone can create their own lending protocol as a Nomos subprotocol without an entry threshold.
subprotocol.subprotocolOwnerText: Earn interest spread in subprotocols. Owners of various levels get varying income in NOMO.
subprotocol.beginnerText: No threshold. Earn 5% of the subprotocol interest spread.
subprotocol.proText:
Rewards depend on NOMO deposited to the DAO Pool: the more and longer you lock NOMO, the higher the boost. Maximum boost is x3 of the Beginner level, i.e. {{number}}, of the subprotocol interest spread.
Calculation Rules
subprotocol.subprotocolUsersText: Currently, only depositors get rewards. In the next upgrade, subprotocol owners will be able to customize depositor and borrower rewards. Rewards are denominated in NOMO.
subprotocol.depositorsText: Earn 5% of the interest spread of the subprotocol you use.
subprotocol.notice: Note: Binding of a user to a subprotocol is a final operation that cannot be undone.
